data.description: TURN KEY CONDITION 3 bedroom ranch with attached 1 car garage! Large yard on quiet street and backing up to Maple Grove golf course! Meadowvale elementary and Whitmer high school! Freshly painted interior and all new flooring throughout! Remodeled eat-in kitchen with updated cabinets, counters, hardware, lighting and faucet! New furnace-2023! Full bathroom remodel with new vanity, flooring, fiberglass tub and surround! 12 x 8 laundry room and tons of attic storage! Service drive to golf course 4 foot easement. Awesome location with beautiful golf course views- BETTER HURRY!
